						               													<description>&amp;#10;     SOLO BALONCESTO  is a two-player boardgame that recreates a real basketball match. Each player is one of the two teams facing-up coaches. Two teams with 10 players each, where you can choose your &amp;quot;starting lineup&amp;quot; on the court:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    point guards&amp;#10;    shooting guards&amp;#10;    small forwards&amp;#10;    power forwards&amp;#10;    centers&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;  &amp;#10;Each player has 5 different skills: Passing - action points - play skill - height -  scoring %.&amp;#10; You have full control of the whole team, which will allow you to perform any individual action with any player on the court. A joint action between two players like a screen or a &amp;quot;pick&amp;amp; roll&amp;quot;, a team tactic like playing in the zone or a man-to-man defense, faithfully recreating what happens in a basketball game. Thanks to its mechanic, mixes a great realism in the actions with high simplicity. Players move one by one alternating between attacker and defender, not the entire team at once, making play faster. This makes the duration of a turn variable, so you play four quarters like in a real game but not a predetermined number of turns in each quarter.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Passes, rebounds, fouls, two-point shots, lay ups, three-pointers, dunks, freethrows, blocks, pick&amp;amp; roll, steals... any basketball action is possible in this game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
